ot;ЖА&quot; до 11.05.2021 г.</p><p>В случае невыполнения работ в установленные сроки будет рассмотрена возможность привлечения к административной ответственности.</p>","author_name":"Администрация Фрунзенского района","performer":null,"response_performers":[],"files":[{"id":16768661,"url":"/storage/2/5666802c-97a2-4094-b9a7-af31d7bcf09d.pdf","original_name":"Справка Купчинская 25-11.pdf"}],"photos":[],"reject":null,"interim_date":"2021-05-11"},"meta":{"title":"Ответ","icon_text":"ПО","icon_title":"Промежуточный ответ","bg_color":"#E3F2FD","border_color":"#536DFE","status_font_color":"#FFFFFF","status_bg_color":"#A5D6A7","icon_bg_color":"#536DFE"},"content_type":28},{"widget":"public.status","key":"changestatus_12308688","payload":{"id":12308688,"dt":"2020-11-17T12:21:50.043981","status_name":"Рассмотрение","status":3},"meta":{"title":"Изменение статуса сообщения","bg_color":"#EEEEEE","icon":"fa-clock-o","icon_bg_color":"#FCAA62"},"content_type":30},{"widget":"public.status","key":"changestatus_12305360","payload":{"id":12305360,"dt":"2020-11-17T08:34:47.636058","status_name":"Модерация","status":1},"meta":{"title":"Изменение статуса сообщения","bg_color":"#EEEEEE","icon":"fa-hand-paper-o","icon_bg_color":"#469ED3"},"content_type":30},{"widget":"public.petition","key":"petition_3348914","payload":{"id":3348914,"dt":"2020-11-17T08:34:47.486728","status_name":"Промежуточный ответ","body":[{"text":"Надписи на стене и двери.","typeof":1}],"photos":[{"url":"/storage/1/fd1958a1-ff57-489b-8347-5da093e1a856.JPG","original_name":"IMG_0805.JPG","id":3809506,"thumbnail":"/media/cache/11/ee/11ee94c79d364e031274ffa107551112.jpg","original_url":"/storage/1/fd1958a1-ff57-489b-8347-5da093e1a856.JPG","size":"932x699"},{"url":"/storage/1/2c34a2c1-5334-4588-9fac-63d7f91f1fb9.JPG","original_name":"IMG_0806.JPG","id":3809507,"thumbnail":"/media/cache/30/03/30034b615bcf90b9a541812246ce4297.jpg","original_url":"/storage/1/2c34a2c1-5334-4588-9fac-63d7f91f1fb9.JPG","size":"4032x3024"}],"file